msgstr "允许为通过 Blesta API 成功认证的用户自动创建 WordPress 帐户。"

msgid "Enter the site key provided by Cloudflare Turnstile for CAPTCHA verification."
msgstr "输入 Cloudflare Turnstile 提供的站点密钥以进行 CAPTCHA 验证。"

